INSTALLATION OF APPIUM and other needed files:

Appium will not run if nodejs/npm are installed as a privileged (sudo) user so use Homebrew instead.

Needed:
>Java Development Kit (JDK)
>Android SDK/ADB
    >Android SDK Packages
>NodeJs
>Microsoft .net Framework
>Appium Desktop Client
>PDaNet
>Eclipse IDE


Phone:
>Enable Developer Options on mobile
>Usb
>Enable Usb thingy 
